{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Launch an independent inquiry into family court\u2019s handling of domestic abuse",
        "additional_details": "We are asking for the inquiry to include:\r\n\uf0a7\tInvestigating decisions made in domestic abuse-related family court cases to identify failures in protecting victims and children.\r\n\uf0a7\tMandatory evidence-based trauma training for all judges and professionals whose assessments influence court outcomes.\r\n\uf0a7\tA full review of the welfare checklist to prioritise child and adult safety over the presumption of contact with an abusive parent.\r\n",
        "background": "We call on the Government to launch an independent inquiry into the family court system regarding their handling of domestic abuse allegations.",
